sk boundary layer and this is used\nto estimate the disk erosion time-scale as $\\sim 1-10^2$ Myr, with the lower\nvalue favored.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jun 2008 20:52:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
